column5: A couple hours and prep will be final.Headed north in the AM. I'll have a Winnipeg river report for you in 12 days.

The rain gear! It's 80 today in Minaki, but showing rain starting tomorrow through Sunday! The Minaki fishing report has been real good for walleye, bass, musky, and pike, with some nice size fish being caught in all species. You're going to have a blast! When you pull out, I will be arriving! I'll probably be passing you on Hwy 596. Unfortunately you'll be going the wrong way!
Good luck, and I'll be checking here on the 18th for the report!
